*shrine_2
@saveon
@fg c=シュバルツ
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ]「Hmm? Are you adventurers?」[k]
There was an adventurer in the rear of the temple.[k]
[シュバルツ]「My name is Schwarz. What are you guys doing here?」[k]
You told him that you were here at the request of the Princess of Sapphire Castle.[k]
[シュバルツ]「When I heard that the Temple of Polaris was being raided, I couldn't stand still.」[k]
[シュバルツ]「...This temple is an important place dedicated to the god Polaris, who brought peace to this world. We must protect it.」[k]
[シュバルツ]「I'd like to ask for your help.」[k]
[シュバルツ]「You see, many monsters are gathered in the room ahead.」[k]
[シュバルツ]「They intend to enter the Hall of the Gods ahead and destroy the altar. We must stop them at all costs.」[k]
[シュバルツ]「When I see an opportunity, I intend to rush into the room and defeat the monsters. Would you guys be willing to fight with me?」[k]
Your objectives are the same. You have decided to accept Schwarz's offer to fight together.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.シュバルツ)'
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>Schwarz joined the party!"
[eventoff]


